author: jpata
body:
Avoid committing .pb files (tensorflow weights) to cms-sw/cmssw. This seems to happen every once in a while, especially for first-time contributors: https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/32222 and https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/32128

No validation was done, no backport is intended.
title: Ignore tensorflow models
